<!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
<section class="block" id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What's inside</span>
      <h2>A complete fundraising shop, beautiful out of the box.</h2>
      <p>Everything you need to launch, run, and track a fundraiser — built right into the store you already have.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-num">01 — Landing pages</span>
        <h3>Beautiful pages, instantly.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Upload your photos and story</li>
          <li>Live progress bar toward goal</li>
          <li>Branded with your products</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="shot">
        <img src="{{ '/resources/img/popup-shop.png' | url }}" alt="Campaign landing page" style="aspect-ratio:4/3;width:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top center;" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-num">02 — Onboarding</span>
        <h3>One link. Zero spreadsheets.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Add campaigns in seconds</li>
          <li>Share one link to onboard everyone</li>
          <li>Works on any device</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="shot">
        <img src="{{ '/resources/img/onboarding.png' | url }}" alt="Fundlet onboarding form" style="aspect-ratio:4/3;width:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top center;" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-num">03 — Tracking</span>
        <h3>Every sale, automatically tracked.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>By campaign, by participant</li>
          <li>Dashboard with live progress</li>
          <li>One-click exportable reports</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="shot">
        <img src="{{ '/resources/img/tracking-dashboard.png' | url }}" alt="Fundlet tracking dashboard" style="aspect-ratio:4/3;width:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:top center;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== HOW IT WORKS ===== -->
<section class="block section-dark" id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h2>A new sales channel for your store, built on community.</h2>
      <p>Fundlet lets organizations — sports teams, schools, churches — sell your products to raise money. You fulfill the orders; everyone wins.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="n">01</div>
        <h4>Create a campaign.</h4>
        <p>Pick a product, set a goal, brand it for your partner. Minutes, not hours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="n">02</div>
        <h4>They sell, you fulfill.</h4>
        <p>Their community shops your store through one link. You handle orders as usual.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="n">03</div>
        <h4>Pay out with confidence.</h4>
        <p>Sales auto-tagged by fundraiser. Export, cut a check, done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== REVIEWS ===== -->
