      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <span class="tag">Peleman Industries</span>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>"It's elegantly simple which I appreciate — nothing added that doesn't need to be there. I tried other apps and solutions; this is the best."</p>
        <div class="who"><b>Peleman Industries</b>Shopify App Store · United States</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <span class="tag">UpTop Treats</span>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>"I searched high and low for an app to allow fundraising for my candy site — this was exactly what I was looking for. Highly recommend."</p>
        <div class="who"><b>UpTop Treats</b>Shopify App Store · United States</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review">
        <span class="tag">A3 Beauty by Arhi</span>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>"From day one, Matt has been flexible, patient, and incredibly thorough. At no point did I feel rushed or dismissed. It's a partnership."</p>
        <div class="who"><b>A3 Beauty by Arhi</b>Shopify App Store · United States</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

